body:
To whom it may concern,

I am writing to ask {{brokerName}} to delete and suppress all personal information you hold about me, and to stop selling or sharing it, to the fullest extent of any applicable data-protection or privacy law.

Name: {{name}}
Also listed under: {{aliases}}
Location: {{location}}
Reply to: {{email}}

Please confirm in writing once this is done, do not re-list this information, and request no more identification from me than is strictly necessary to process this request.

Thank you.
